Base: 0.30N TMAH (in DIW)
Additives:
  → 4.0% w/w Surfynol 440 (wetting agent)
  → 0.1% w/w Tetramethylammonium Lactate (TMAL — dissolution enhancer)

Mixing Protocol:
  → Prepare fresh every 12 hours.
  → Filter through 0.05 µm PTFE membrane before use.
  → Store under N₂ atmosphere. Shelf life: 24 hours.
